thread.title: BRIEF-Spain's Abengoa wins 38 mln euro construction contract in Denmark
thread.title_full: BRIEF-Spain's Abengoa wins 38 mln euro construction contract in Denmark | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Spain's Abengoa wins 38 mln euro construction contract in Denmark
text:
Sept 10 Spain's Abengoa :
* Says it has been awarded a building and engineering contract for a new hospital complex in Denmark worth 38 million euros ($42.6 million)
* Says the project will last 24 months Further company coverage: ($1 = 0.8921 euros) (Reporting by Madrid Newsroom)
